ndulum-like device. There once was an incident in which it took  away a child it hypnotized."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"When it locks eyes with an enemy, it will use a mix of PSI moves such as HYPNOSIS and CONFUSION."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Seeing its swinging pendulum can induce sleep in three seconds, even in someone who just woke up."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Seeing its swinging pendulum can induce sleep in three seconds, even in someone who just woke up."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Seeing its swinging pendulum can induce sleep in three seconds, even in someone who just woke up."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"When it is very hungry, it puts humans it meets to sleep, then it feasts on their dreams."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Always holding a pendulum that it swings at a steady rhythm, it causes drowsiness in anyone nearby."},{"version":"black","text":"Seeing its swinging pendulum can induce sleep in three seconds, even in someone who just woke up."},{"version":"white","text":"Seeing its swinging pendulum can induce sleep in three seconds, even in someone who just woke up."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Seeing its swinging pendulum can induce sleep in three seconds, even in someone who just woke up."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Seeing its swinging pendulum can induce sleep in three seconds, even in someone who just woke up."},{"version":"x","text":"It carries a pendulum-like device. There once was an incident in which it took away a child it hypnotized."},{"version":"y","text":"Seeing its swinging pendulum can induce sleep in three seconds, even in someone who just woke up."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Hypno holds a pendulum in its hand. The arcing movement and glitter of the pendulum lull the foe into a deep state of hypnosis. While this Pok\u00e9mon searches for prey, it polishes the pendulum."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Hypno holds a pendulum in its hand. The arcing movement and glitter of the pendulum lull the foe into a deep state of hypnosis. While this Pok\u00e9mon searches for prey, it polishes the pendulum."},{"version":"sun","text":"While it is an extremely dangerous Pok\u00e9mon, people who are in need of a good, sound sleep call it their savior."},{"version":"moon","text":"As a matter of course, it makes anyone it meets fall asleep and has a taste of their dreams. Anyone having a good dream, it carries off."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"In Alola, Komala is Hypno\u2019s main target. It rarely harms people."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"There are some Hypno that assist doctors with patients who can\u2019t sleep at night in hospitals."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Avoid eye contact if you come across one. It will try to put you to sleep by using its pendulum."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Avoid eye contact if you come across one. It will try to put you to sleep by using its pendulum."}],"evo":{"name":"drowzee","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"hypno","level":1,"min_level":26,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/97.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/97.png","capture":75,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"special_defense":2},"forms":[]}